data.description: Welcome to 6490 Manning Road, a charming residence located on the outskirts of Miamisburg OH. This beautifully maintained home offers a perfect blend of modern comforts and classic charm, making it an ideal haven for your family. Features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath   with 1.5 acre. Dont miss the opportunity to own such a beautiful home! Fireplace is not warranted. Call me today for a showing!
